HEADWORD: monomeric
<hw>mon`o*mer"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<def>Not linked to other molecules of the same kind; having the property
of a monomer. Opposed to <ant>polymeric</ant>.</def>⟦br⟧
